{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_15_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "このリボン、誰かの落とし物か？\n……まぁいいか、俺の方でツリーに飾り付けておこう",
      "startTime": 5.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3838.3218130999994,
          "startTime": 8.9716551464
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、{user}さん\n今回のライブのことで唯もお礼を言いたいって……",
      "startTime": 10.8649883271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "な、何を持っているんですか、それは！？\nそのリボンで、何をするつもりですか！？",
      "startTime": 18.6316549938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "何って、飾り付けだが……\n飾り付け用のリボンなんだから、当然だろう？",
      "startTime": 24.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……いいえ、その気がないとしても\nリボンを手にしてしまった以上、野放しには出来ません",
      "startTime": 30.7976639431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私はここ数日で学んだんです\n細長いものはハレンチを呼ぶ、と！",
      "startTime": 37.6976639431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どんな格言なんだそれは！？\n大丈夫だ、ツリーに飾り付けるだけだから……",
      "startTime": 42.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、そのリボンを渡して下さい！\n最悪の事態になる前に！",
      "startTime": 49.3989775342,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2745.1665242999966,
          "startTime": 52.1441440585
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5201.025263299996,
          "startTime": 54.6000027975
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待ってくれ怜！　古手川さんも！\nいきなり暴れたら……あっ……！",
      "startTime": 54.3506387808,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6094.691743900001,
          "startTime": 60.4453305247
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_tail-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5428.0250772000045,
          "startTime": 59.778663858
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7428.0250772000045,
          "startTime": 61.778663858
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "よし、これでハレンチからみんなを守ることが……\nって、きゃあああっ！？",
      "startTime": 60.7119971914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "怜！　古手川さん！　大丈夫か！？\n転んで怪我とかしていないか！？",
      "startTime": 65.8333356223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いたた……だ、大丈夫です……\nえ？　な、なんですか、これー！？",
      "startTime": 78.3619963967,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3745.0126009000114,
          "startTime": 82.1070089976
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5130.589199100001,
          "startTime": 83.4925855958
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7033.333333400009,
          "startTime": 85.3953297301
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8492.901102700003,
          "startTime": 86.8548974994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "リボンが私と唯の体に絡まって……\nな、何をどうしたらこんな絡まり方をするんですか！",
      "startTime": 85.2953297301,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "だ、だから細長いものは危ないって言ったのに！\n……いえ、もしかして、最初からこれが狙い！？",
      "startTime": 94.3091169227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "飾り付けたいって、私達を飾り付けたいって\n意味だったんですね！？",
      "startTime": 103.6286630634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "違う！　俺はそんなつもりはない！\nこれはただの事故だ！　信じてくれ！",
      "startTime": 107.7645402292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "このハレンチマネージャー！　ケダモノ！\nこの状況でそんな言い訳が通用すると思いますか！？",
      "startTime": 113.5553295775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "本当に誤解なんだって！\nと、とにかくリボンを解くから……！",
      "startTime": 119.1000043235,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2579.1431743000003,
          "startTime": 121.6791474978
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3964.719772500004,
          "startTime": 123.064724096
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5198.053105900001,
          "startTime": 124.2980574294
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6431.386439199997,
          "startTime": 125.5313907627
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "きゃーっ！　もっと絡んできてます！\nよ、余計なことをしないで下さーい！",
      "startTime": 124.964724096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 128.9924747466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 130.0591409046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "ここの振り付けはもっとこう……！\n次はこうで、もっと激しく……！",
      "startTime": 135.0980513259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、怜\nライブが終わったばかりなのに頑張っているな",
      "startTime": 140.0333427431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！　お疲れ様です\n……あの、この間はすみませんでした",
      "startTime": 147.0647177064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "冷静になるべきだと反省したばかりだったのに\nあんなに責めてしまって……",
      "startTime": 154.9980571433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "誤解が解けて良かったよ\n危うく社会的に抹殺されるところだったからな",
      "startTime": 159.5666760764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……本当にごめんなさい……\nあの時は動揺と恥ずかしさで、つい……",
      "startTime": 167.7723819101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "まさかみんなの前で\nあんな姿を晒すことになるだなんて……うぅ……",
      "startTime": 173.8335665059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "その様子だと、まだハレンチを警戒する癖は\n抜けていないみたいだな",
      "startTime": 182.4666760764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "はい……おかげさまで最近はそういう想像自体は\nだいぶ収まってきているんですけど……",
      "startTime": 189.2094339376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "ララ達がいなくなって静かになったはずなのに\nまだハレンチを警戒しちゃって……",
      "startTime": 195.1427672709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、トラブルだらけで大変だったけど\nとても楽しかったですよね",
      "startTime": 201.1761006043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。他のみんなも楽しそうだったし\nまたいつか一緒に過ごせるといいな",
      "startTime": 207.2666760764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_03-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "今度はハレンチなことが起きないようにしたいですね\n……{user}さんに飾り付けられたりとか",
      "startTime": 214.2269166316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
